50|$|Since {{the early}} 2000s, <b>Stableford's</b> {{photographs}} {{have appeared in}} The New York Times, The Washington Post, USA Today, The Atlantic, Sports Illustrated, National Geographic Adventure, Oprah, Newsweek, Men's Journal, Men's Health, Sunset, and Reader's Digest, among other national publications.|$|R
